1
00:00:35,637 --> 00:00:38,577
<font face="Qlassik Bold" size="40"> <font color="#181a72">ELEVATION</font></font>

2
00:00:42,637 --> 00:00:46,157
<font face="Qlassik Bold" size="40"><font color="#c2d5d8">AKINA-CHO</font></font>

3
00:00:42,637 --> 00:00:46,157
<font face="Qlassik Bold" size="40"><font color="#153215">AKINA LAKE</font></font>

4
00:00:55,347 --> 00:00:56,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">This time already ?</font>

5
00:00:57,207 --> 00:00:59,897
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I must have gotten carried away.
 I'd better head home.</font>

6
00:01:08,657 --> 00:01:10,027
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">W...what was that ?!</font>

7
00:01:31,007 --> 00:01:38,407
<font face="Georgia" size="48" color="#ffff00"><b><font color="#ffffff">- Awakening -</font></b></font>

8
00:01:31,107 --> 00:01:38,407
<font face="Georgia" size="48" color="#ffff00"><b><i><font color="#ffffff">New Movie [Initial]</font></i></b></font>

9
00:01:31,107 --> 00:01:38,407
<font face="Qlassik Bold" size="40"><i><font color="#ffffff">Central Anime</font></i></font>

10
00:01:44,107 --> 00:01:45,977
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">He's still on my tail, and I can't shake him.</font></font>

11
00:01:47,207 --> 00:01:48,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Is this a bad dream or what ?</font></font>

12
00:01:49,257 --> 00:01:53,477
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Even though this's my first time on this mountain pass, 
someone like me shouldn't be pushed like this.</font></font>

13
00:01:54,477 --> 00:01:56,927
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">This ain't funny, dammit !</font></font>

14
00:02:02,407 --> 00:02:03,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">You can't do it !</font></font>

15
00:02:03,407 --> 00:02:05,827
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">There's a sharp left hander
 ahead of this slow left curve.</font></font>

16
00:02:09,107 --> 00:02:11,237
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Your tail is sliding out because of the inertia.</font></font>

17
00:02:11,237 --> 00:02:13,827
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">You're going too fast, 
there's no margin for recovery.</font></font>

18
00:02:16,307 --> 00:02:17,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">What the...?!</font></font>

19
00:02:20,507 --> 00:02:21,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">An Eight-Six ?</font></font>

20
00:02:24,187 --> 00:02:25,957
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Is that really an Eight-Six ?</font></font>

21
00:02:50,187 --> 00:02:51,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Are you alright ?</font>

22
00:02:51,657 --> 00:02:52,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You hurt ?</font>

23
00:02:53,687 --> 00:02:58,267
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Did I just see the ghost of a
dead Mt. Akina street racer ?</font>

24
00:02:59,617 --> 00:03:02,527
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That was a frustratingly perfect super drift.</font>

25
00:03:04,277 --> 00:03:08,347
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What the hell was with that Eight-Six ?</font>

26
00:03:12,657 --> 00:03:16,727
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Seriously, Iketani's story sounded awesome.</font>

27
00:03:16,727 --> 00:03:18,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It gave me the chills.</font>

28
00:03:18,907 --> 00:03:23,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">An Eight-Six owned an RX-7 on Akina.</font>

29
00:03:23,007 --> 00:03:27,287
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Even on the downhill, an Eight-Six beat a pure sports machine like the Seven.</font>

30
00:03:28,627 --> 00:03:31,387
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Hey, Takumi, are you listening ?</font>

31
00:03:31,387 --> 00:03:32,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I am.</font>

32
00:03:32,607 --> 00:03:35,197
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So what's an Eight-Six ?</font>

33
00:03:36,197 --> 00:03:37,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's a car...a car.</font>

34
00:03:39,467 --> 00:03:41,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's a weird name.</font>

35
00:03:41,007 --> 00:03:42,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Who makes it ? Mazda ?</font>

36
00:03:44,357 --> 00:03:49,267
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You don't know what an Eight-Six is,
 even though you work at a gas station ?</font>

37
00:03:49,267 --> 00:03:52,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">An Eight-Six is a Toyota, 
and it's more than a decade old.</font>

38
00:03:53,737 --> 00:03:55,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That doesn't sound all that good.</font>

39
00:03:55,557 --> 00:03:58,587
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Even Dad has an old Toyota for work.</font>

40
00:03:58,587 --> 00:04:00,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You can't compare it with that.</font>

41
00:04:00,657 --> 00:04:03,487
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The Eight-Six is special, even if it's old.</font>

42
00:04:04,757 --> 00:04:05,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I've decided.</font>

43
00:04:05,707 --> 00:04:08,357
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'll look for a used Eight-Six, instead of a Silvia.</font>

44
00:04:08,907 --> 00:04:11,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Is the Eight-Six easier to buy ?</font>

45
00:04:12,077 --> 00:04:13,297
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Nope.</font>

46
00:04:13,857 --> 00:04:16,697
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I thought so, especially with our pay.</font>

47
00:04:18,457 --> 00:04:21,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The best a high school student can 
make would be what, about 120,000 yen ? {about 1,000 USD}</font>

48
00:04:22,507 --> 00:04:25,017
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You guys have a job ?</font>

49
00:04:28,107 --> 00:04:31,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What's wrong ? Is it that strange
 for me to strike up a conversation ?</font>

50
00:04:34,907 --> 00:04:37,747
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So, you make 120,000 yen a month ?</font>

51
00:04:37,747 --> 00:04:40,487
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yeah, for 8 hours a day, 6 days a week.</font>

52
00:04:40,487 --> 00:04:42,857
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What ? That long ?</font>

53
00:04:42,857 --> 00:04:45,617
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You only get 120,000 for working so long ?</font>

54
00:04:46,717 --> 00:04:47,997
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's normal, isn't it ?</font>

55
00:04:49,657 --> 00:04:51,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Unless you have a different sense of money.</font>

56
00:04:53,777 --> 00:04:57,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Good luck. Why don't we go 
somewhere and have fun after finals, okay ?</font>

57
00:05:01,707 --> 00:05:03,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What's with her...?</font>

58
00:05:03,607 --> 00:05:06,687
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's been a year since
 I last talked to Mogi Natsuki.{ last time.}</font>

59
00:05:07,397 --> 00:05:13,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I used to talk to her often when I was in the soccer club, because she was a manager.</font>

60
00:05:13,107 --> 00:05:15,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">But one day, I got in wrong with her.</font>

61
00:05:16,727 --> 00:05:18,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What did you do ?</font>

62
00:05:19,527 --> 00:05:22,747
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I beat up a senior, who just
 happened to be her boyfriend.</font>

63
00:05:23,567 --> 00:05:26,637
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You beat up a senior in the soccer club ?</font>

64
00:05:26,637 --> 00:05:28,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I had a reason.</font>

65
00:05:29,297 --> 00:05:32,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You've been like that since you were little.</font>

66
00:05:32,757 --> 00:05:37,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You normally look like a sleepyhead,
 but you change when you snap.</font>

67
00:05:37,767 --> 00:05:41,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You know those wimpy elementary school kids ?</font>

68
00:05:41,207 --> 00:05:44,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The type who gets really strong after crying ?</font>

69
00:05:45,117 --> 00:05:47,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I was like that.</font>

70
00:05:54,507 --> 00:05:57,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So you're looking for an Eight-Six, huh ?</font>

71
00:05:57,207 --> 00:05:59,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You have good taste, Itsuki.</font>

72
00:05:59,207 --> 00:06:01,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Don't I ?
 You think so too, Iketani ?</font>

73
00:06:02,257 --> 00:06:06,237
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Your parents have a car, right ?
 Why don't you borrow it ?</font>

74
00:06:06,237 --> 00:06:07,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's no good.</font>

75
00:06:07,007 --> 00:06:11,697
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">My dad's car is a diesel-powered
 FF with an auto tranny.</font>

76
00:06:11,697 --> 00:06:14,297
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Only FR cars are real cars.</font>

77
00:06:14,297 --> 00:06:18,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">If it's got four wheels,
 and is drivable, it's a car.</font>

78
00:06:18,107 --> 00:06:19,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You don't get it, do you ?</font>

79
00:06:19,707 --> 00:06:23,727
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The car has no value if you
 can't enjoy it on the mountain pass.</font>

80
00:06:23,727 --> 00:06:25,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You bring that up so often.</font>

81
00:06:25,657 --> 00:06:27,727
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What do you do in the mountain pass ?</font>

82
00:06:27,727 --> 00:06:29,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Do what ?</font>

83
00:06:29,007 --> 00:06:32,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Isn't it obvious ?
Drive hard in the corners.</font>

84
00:06:33,807 --> 00:06:35,837
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Is it fun doing that ?</font>

85
00:06:35,837 --> 00:06:36,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Wha...?</font>

86
00:06:36,657 --> 00:06:38,057
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Of course it's fun !</font>

87
00:06:38,787 --> 00:06:42,847
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Guys love to push it hard
 on mountain passes in style.</font>

88
00:06:42,847 --> 00:06:44,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Right, Iketani ?</font>

89
00:06:44,207 --> 00:06:46,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yeah, I like it.</font>

90
00:06:46,457 --> 00:06:48,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's why I have a team.</font>

91
00:06:48,007 --> 00:06:51,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">When I get an Eight-Six, 
can I join the Akina Speed Stars ?</font>

92
00:06:51,657 --> 00:06:53,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I've been dreaming about that for so long.</font>

93
00:06:54,497 --> 00:06:55,217
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Welcome !</font>

94
00:06:56,397 --> 00:06:57,197
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Welcome...</font>

95
00:07:00,007 --> 00:07:01,217
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">An RX-7.</font>

96
00:07:03,897 --> 00:07:05,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Red Suns...?!</font>

97
00:07:05,657 --> 00:07:06,357
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Could it be...</font>

98
00:07:07,007 --> 00:07:09,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The yellow FD of the Red Suns. {TEXT Rotary Brothers!}</font>

99
00:07:09,087 --> 00:07:09,807
<font face="Qlassik Bold" size="40"><font color="#ff0000">Rotary Brothers !</font></font>

100
00:07:09,657 --> 00:07:12,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I knew it. 
That's Takahashi Keisuke.</font>

101
00:07:12,457 --> 00:07:13,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Is he famous ?</font>

102
00:07:13,657 --> 00:07:14,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yeah.</font>

103
00:07:14,457 --> 00:07:19,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He's number 2 of the Akagi Red Suns,
 which is even recognized by some pros.</font>

104
00:07:20,147 --> 00:07:24,927
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He's Keisuke, the younger one of the Takahashi brothers, 
who are the fastest on Akagi with their rotary-powered cars.</font>

105
00:07:28,157 --> 00:07:29,927
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So we meet again.</font>

106
00:07:29,927 --> 00:07:32,057
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So it's your S13, after all.</font>

107
00:07:33,237 --> 00:07:35,217
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">High octane, right ?</font>

108
00:07:35,217 --> 00:07:36,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yeah.</font>

109
00:07:36,007 --> 00:07:37,567
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Fill it up with the high octane !</font>

110
00:07:37,567 --> 00:07:38,647
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yes, right.</font>

111
00:07:46,337 --> 00:07:49,777
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Oh man, does he want to fly ?</font></font>

112
00:07:50,557 --> 00:07:52,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I have to ask you one more time.</font>

113
00:07:52,307 --> 00:07:57,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You really don't know anything
 about that Eight-Six I saw on Akina ?</font>

114
00:07:59,157 --> 00:08:00,057
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">No.</font>

115
00:08:01,007 --> 00:08:05,057
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">What ? So an Eight-Six really
 did beat Takahashi Keisuke ?</font></font>

116
00:08:05,907 --> 00:08:09,927
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">How come the locals don't
 know about a car like that ?</font>

117
00:08:09,927 --> 00:08:12,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">No matter how many times
 you ask, I just don't know.</font>

118
00:08:12,907 --> 00:08:13,927
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I see.</font>

119
00:08:14,357 --> 00:08:15,617
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Cap is okay.</font>

120
00:08:17,607 --> 00:08:19,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Anything else today ? {literally, "which direction today," but I had to adapt here. Japanese gas station attendants kindly stop the traffic for you.}</font>

121
00:08:20,987 --> 00:08:22,637
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'll repay my debt to the ghost.</font>

122
00:08:33,007 --> 00:08:36,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That Takahashi Keisuke is intimidating.</font>

123
00:08:45,707 --> 00:08:46,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What ?!</font>

124
00:08:46,907 --> 00:08:49,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You're going to take me to Mt. Akina ?</font>

125
00:08:49,557 --> 00:08:51,527
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yeah, next Saturday.</font>

126
00:08:51,527 --> 00:08:52,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Alright !</font>

127
00:08:52,657 --> 00:08:54,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'll go.
 I'll go, no matter what.</font>

128
00:08:54,707 --> 00:08:58,097
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You, too. Right, right ?</font>

129
00:08:58,097 --> 00:08:59,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Y...yeah.</font>

130
00:09:00,357 --> 00:09:02,827
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">A chance like this doesn't come often.</font>

131
00:09:02,827 --> 00:09:05,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'll be able to meet the 
members of the Akina Speed Stars.</font>

132
00:09:06,987 --> 00:09:08,697
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I can't wait for Saturday.</font>

133
00:09:18,707 --> 00:09:19,787
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'm home.</font>

134
00:09:21,287 --> 00:09:22,237
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Supper ?</font>

135
00:09:22,237 --> 00:09:23,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Already ate.</font>

136
00:09:24,307 --> 00:09:26,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You're so unsociable.</font>

137
00:09:26,007 --> 00:09:27,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Look who's talking.</font>

138
00:09:35,227 --> 00:09:40,077
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#8ffeff">Good luck. Why don't we go 
somewhere and have fun after finals, okay ?</font></font>

139
00:09:42,727 --> 00:09:44,857
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">What's gotten into her ?</font></font>

140
00:09:47,207 --> 00:09:48,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Oh, whatever.</font>

141
00:09:48,907 --> 00:09:50,927
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I've got to wake up early.
I should get some sleep.</font>

142
00:10:01,657 --> 00:10:03,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Alright, the next left curve is...</font>

143
00:10:07,137 --> 00:10:11,567
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">That bastard must be local because he
 seemed so familiar with Akina's mountain pass.</font></font>

144
00:10:12,387 --> 00:10:14,937
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Otherwise, how could 
I have lost to an Eight-Six ?</font></font>

145
00:10:20,387 --> 00:10:24,897
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">I want to meet him again.
 I can't be satisfied until I get my revenge.</font></font>

146
00:10:25,637 --> 00:10:27,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Come out, ghost of Akina !</font></font>

147
00:10:29,107 --> 00:10:32,077
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">I've come here to meet you !</font></font>

148
00:10:48,907 --> 00:10:51,097
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's no joke, seriously.</font>

149
00:10:51,357 --> 00:10:53,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That outsider every night...</font>

150
00:10:53,207 --> 00:10:56,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Akina is the home ground
 our team, the Speed Stars !</font>

151
00:10:56,657 --> 00:10:59,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We're not Takahashi Keisuke's target.</font>

152
00:10:59,657 --> 00:11:02,437
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">A panda-colored Eight-Six, right ?</font>

153
00:11:02,437 --> 00:11:08,587
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Don't get me wrong, but I can't believe your
 story about such a super-fast Eight-Six on Akina.</font>

154
00:11:08,587 --> 00:11:09,687
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">There is one !</font>

155
00:11:10,407 --> 00:11:11,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Oh, Mr. Tachibana...</font>

156
00:11:11,307 --> 00:11:12,237
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Hello. {Another guy:  Hello.}</font>

157
00:11:13,037 --> 00:11:18,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">When I was actively street racing, there was the fastest driver, whose speed on Akina was recognized by everyone.</font>

158
00:11:18,907 --> 00:11:23,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Our team also claims 
to be the fastest on Akina.</font>

159
00:11:23,007 --> 00:11:27,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">There are lots of self-proclaimed "fastest," 
but this guy was the real deal.</font>

160
00:11:27,767 --> 00:11:31,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">On top of that, he still
 drives on Akina even today.</font>

161
00:11:32,137 --> 00:11:33,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Even today ?</font>

162
00:11:33,157 --> 00:11:36,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We know most of Akina's street racers, so...</font>

163
00:11:37,117 --> 00:11:42,967
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He drives at odd times because
 he's a tofu shop owner now.</font>

164
00:11:42,967 --> 00:11:43,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What ?!</font>

165
00:11:43,907 --> 00:11:46,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">A legendary street racer has
 become a tofu shopkeeper ?</font>

166
00:11:46,587 --> 00:11:52,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He delivers tofu from the mountain base to a hotel at Akina Lake around 4 am...</font>

167
00:11:52,257 --> 00:11:53,397
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">...with his Eight-Six.</font>

168
00:11:54,747 --> 00:12:00,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's his job, so he drives every day, 
in the rain or even snow.</font>

169
00:12:00,457 --> 00:12:04,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He knows everything about Akina's 
mountain pass, even all the stains on the asphalt.</font>

170
00:12:04,907 --> 00:12:09,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{karami}Once he's unloaded the tofu, he drives down the pass at an incredible speed.</font>

171
00:12:09,207 --> 00:12:11,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'd bet you 10,000,000 yen.</font>

172
00:12:11,257 --> 00:12:16,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The fastest on Akina is the
 tofu shopkeeper's Eight-Six.</font>

173
00:12:16,717 --> 00:12:19,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Tofu shopkeeper's Eight-Six...</font>

174
00:12:25,587 --> 00:12:27,827
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Hello, Fujiwara Tofu Shop.</font>

175
00:12:27,827 --> 00:12:31,667
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Oh, Yuichi. 
What's the matter ?</font>

176
00:12:32,287 --> 00:12:36,367
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Nothing really. I was just curious 
about how you've been doing.</font>

177
00:12:36,367 --> 00:12:38,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#8ffeff">Same ol', same ol'.</font></font>

178
00:12:38,897 --> 00:12:39,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I see.</font>

179
00:12:40,907 --> 00:12:43,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I've heard your Eight-Six is still kicking.</font>

180
00:12:44,157 --> 00:12:47,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#8ffeff">A kid at my station said
 he saw you on the mountain.</font></font>

181
00:12:48,317 --> 00:12:53,857
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#8ffeff">It sounded like you toyed around with 
an RX-7, but aren't you too old for that ?</font></font>

182
00:12:53,857 --> 00:12:55,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You're mistaken. That wasn't me.</font>

183
00:12:56,107 --> 00:13:01,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#8ffeff">How could I be ? Only you drive an 
Eight-Six on Mt. Akina in the morning.</font></font>

184
00:13:01,707 --> 00:13:06,357
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's certainly my car, but I'm
 not the one who delivers tofu now.</font>

185
00:13:09,557 --> 00:13:10,587
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What did you say ?</font>

186
00:13:22,257 --> 00:13:24,727
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Don't spill it, or the tofu will be squished.</font>

187
00:13:25,507 --> 00:13:27,847
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I know, like I've heard that million times.</font>

188
00:13:33,207 --> 00:13:34,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'm off.</font>

189
00:14:04,007 --> 00:14:05,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Let's see...</font>

190
00:14:37,507 --> 00:14:39,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Man, I'm so excited.</font>

191
00:14:39,407 --> 00:14:42,987
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Why isn't it Saturday already ?
 My heart is pounding.</font>

192
00:14:44,057 --> 00:14:45,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Is that so ?</font>

193
00:14:45,887 --> 00:14:49,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You look as sleepy as usual.{ always.}</font>

194
00:14:49,557 --> 00:14:50,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Leave me alone.</font>

195
00:14:51,007 --> 00:14:54,347
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Actually, I am sleepy.</font>

196
00:14:56,167 --> 00:14:58,887
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Don't forget about this Saturday, Takumi.</font>

197
00:14:58,887 --> 00:15:01,597
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I got it. You're so persistent.</font>

198
00:15:03,457 --> 00:15:04,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Lucky.</font>

199
00:15:05,767 --> 00:15:08,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Takumi, good morning.</font>

200
00:15:08,107 --> 00:15:09,057
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Mogi...</font>

201
00:15:09,057 --> 00:15:10,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Good timing.</font>

202
00:15:10,657 --> 00:15:12,897
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Do you have a minute ?</font>

203
00:15:12,897 --> 00:15:14,317
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">S...sure.</font>

204
00:15:14,317 --> 00:15:15,587
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Come with me.</font>

205
00:15:18,787 --> 00:15:19,827
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'd better go.</font>

206
00:15:22,607 --> 00:15:25,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What's going on ?
 I thought Mogi hated you.</font>

207
00:15:29,307 --> 00:15:32,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I've been thinking...</font>

208
00:15:33,757 --> 00:15:39,267
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I think it's time to restore our friendship.</font>

209
00:15:39,267 --> 00:15:41,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">There's nothing to restore.</font>

210
00:15:41,907 --> 00:15:44,887
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I wasn't at odds with you.</font>

211
00:15:44,887 --> 00:15:47,057
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So you're okay with it ?</font>

212
00:15:47,057 --> 00:15:48,087
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'm so glad.</font>

213
00:15:52,907 --> 00:15:56,057
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You were talking about 
cars the other day, right ?</font>

214
00:15:56,057 --> 00:15:58,647
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Can you drive ?</font>

215
00:15:58,647 --> 00:15:59,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yeah.</font>

216
00:15:59,307 --> 00:16:04,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Then would you go for a drive with 
me sometime during summer break ?</font>

217
00:16:04,557 --> 00:16:08,357
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'll fix some lunch. It'll definitely be fun.</font>

218
00:16:08,357 --> 00:16:11,057
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Fine by me, but the
 car is a piece of junk.</font>

219
00:16:11,057 --> 00:16:13,627
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's just a clunker for work.</font>

220
00:16:13,627 --> 00:16:15,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's alright.</font>

221
00:16:15,657 --> 00:16:18,357
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I don't mind what kind of car it is.</font>

222
00:16:21,317 --> 00:16:24,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Let's go somewhere far away.</font>

223
00:16:24,307 --> 00:16:27,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The beach would be nice.
The two of us can go swimming.</font>

224
00:16:27,707 --> 00:16:29,027
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The two of us...?</font>

225
00:16:29,027 --> 00:16:29,817
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yup.</font>

226
00:16:38,257 --> 00:16:45,017
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">I wonder why she looks so sexy...</font></font>

227
00:16:55,657 --> 00:16:58,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The first right counter steer wasn't a mistake.</font>

228
00:16:56,787 --> 00:16:58,607
<font face="Qlassik Bold" size="40">Takahashi</font>

229
00:16:59,007 --> 00:17:01,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It was a feint motion for the next move.</font>

230
00:17:01,257 --> 00:17:07,887
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{kono}If you steer from inside to outside in that state, the body will instantly roll to the outside...</font>

231
00:17:07,887 --> 00:17:10,767
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{over steer}...which induces over steering to enter a drift.</font>

232
00:17:11,687 --> 00:17:14,057
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I see. That makes sense.</font>

233
00:17:16,337 --> 00:17:19,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's not a drift for show, but for driving fast.</font>

234
00:17:20,477 --> 00:17:24,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That Eight-Six might become useful for the research paper I'm currently working on.</font>

235
00:17:24,507 --> 00:17:26,357
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Who the hell is the driver ?</font>

236
00:17:26,357 --> 00:17:30,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">None of the Red Suns members
 can pull that off, except for you.</font>

237
00:17:30,457 --> 00:17:33,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What are you talking about ? 
You do that, too.</font>

238
00:17:33,307 --> 00:17:34,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Wha...me ?</font>

239
00:17:34,807 --> 00:17:36,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You're weird.</font>

240
00:17:36,407 --> 00:17:39,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You can go neck and neck 
with me without really thinking.</font>

241
00:17:40,457 --> 00:17:44,397
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It would be ideal if you could
 add my logic to your driving.</font>

242
00:17:45,407 --> 00:17:48,977
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Your analytical skills are extraordinary.</font>

243
00:17:49,657 --> 00:17:54,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Just by following your opponent in a
 pair of left and right handers in a battle...</font>

244
00:17:52,907 --> 00:17:54,907
<font face="Qlassik Bold" size="40"> <font color="#4f4b4b">Regenerative Medicine{?}</font></font>

245
00:17:52,907 --> 00:17:54,907
<font face="Qlassik Bold" size="40"> <font color="#4f4b4b">Power to Revolutionize Medical Science</font></font>

246
00:17:54,007 --> 00:18:00,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{aite}...you can figure out your opponent's habits, weaknesses, 
the car's suspension settings and even the engine power...</font>

247
00:18:00,457 --> 00:18:02,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You're a fiend of some sort.</font>

248
00:18:02,547 --> 00:18:04,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Screw this.
 I don't understand this at all.</font>

249
00:18:05,807 --> 00:18:07,047
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's fine.</font>

250
00:18:08,607 --> 00:18:11,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'll go to Akina next Saturday.</font>

251
00:18:11,857 --> 00:18:14,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Finally, you're going to race ?</font>

252
00:18:14,707 --> 00:18:17,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's why I sent you to Akina....</font>

253
00:18:18,437 --> 00:18:22,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">...to make the Akagi Red Suns, and the names of Takahashi Ryosuke and Keisuke become legend.</font>

254
00:18:23,207 --> 00:18:26,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{Kanto}Let's start a project to become
 the fastest in the Kanto Plain.</font>

255
00:18:39,567 --> 00:18:43,027
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Quiet, Takumi !
 You're distracting Iketani !</font>

256
00:18:43,027 --> 00:18:44,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">But it's so scary.</font>

257
00:18:44,607 --> 00:18:46,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That doesn't come as any surprise.</font>

258
00:18:46,207 --> 00:18:50,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Anyone would be scared to ride in 
the car of a street racer for the first time.</font>

259
00:18:50,007 --> 00:18:52,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The next will be a hairpin 
curve in the second gear.</font>

260
00:18:54,507 --> 00:18:56,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Please, stop !</font>

261
00:18:56,707 --> 00:18:58,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I said, shut up !</font>

262
00:19:05,657 --> 00:19:09,077
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Sorry. I guess I got too 
excited and pushed too hard.</font>

263
00:19:09,077 --> 00:19:13,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You're so pathetic, Takumi.
 Man up, already, you wimp.</font>

264
00:19:13,907 --> 00:19:17,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{omae}You must be one of those who cries
 out on a roller coaster, aren't you ?</font>

265
00:19:17,507 --> 00:19:21,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I've never thought a roller coaster was scary.</font>

266
00:19:22,557 --> 00:19:27,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You won't understand this sense
 of fear even if I try to explain.</font>

267
00:19:28,917 --> 00:19:30,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What're you talking about ?</font>

268
00:19:30,807 --> 00:19:31,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">There.</font>

269
00:19:32,107 --> 00:19:33,827
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">See all the guys gathered up ahead ?</font>

270
00:19:36,047 --> 00:19:37,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Something's wrong.</font>

271
00:19:49,127 --> 00:19:50,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Iketani.</font>

272
00:19:50,307 --> 00:19:51,817
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What's wrong, guys ?</font>

273
00:19:51,817 --> 00:19:52,637
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Hey.</font>

274
00:19:55,357 --> 00:19:57,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We're using the course for a bit.</font>

275
00:19:57,407 --> 00:19:58,977
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">My brother is with me today.</font>

276
00:20:00,787 --> 00:20:03,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'm Takahashi Ryosuke. 
Sorry for barging in without notice.</font>

277
00:20:05,257 --> 00:20:08,097
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Ryosuke, the older brother 
of the Takahashi Rotary Brothers.</font>

278
00:20:09,097 --> 00:20:11,347
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">A pair of new and old RX-7s.</font>

279
00:20:12,097 --> 00:20:14,047
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So they're the real Takahashi brothers.</font>

280
00:20:14,527 --> 00:20:17,447
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So they're the Akagi Red Suns.</font>

281
00:20:20,077 --> 00:20:21,697
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What brought you to Akina ?</font>

282
00:20:21,697 --> 00:20:23,357
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's because...</font>

283
00:20:24,397 --> 00:20:25,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Head of PR, your turn.</font>

284
00:20:25,707 --> 00:20:26,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Okay.</font>

285
00:20:26,607 --> 00:20:35,637
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We just discussed the possibility of having a joint event between the Akina Speed Stars and Akagi Red Suns right here next Saturday.</font>

286
00:20:35,637 --> 00:20:36,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Joint event ?</font>

287
00:20:36,607 --> 00:20:37,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yes.</font>

288
00:20:38,077 --> 00:20:40,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We belong to each of our
 teams because we love to race.</font>

289
00:20:40,707 --> 00:20:47,337
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{tama}I think we can improve our skills through stimulating interactions with other teams every now and then.</font>

290
00:20:47,337 --> 00:20:48,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{hajime}At first, we drive around all together.</font>

291
00:20:48,707 --> 00:20:52,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{saigo}At the end, we select two representatives from
 each team for a time attack on the uphill and downhill.</font>

292
00:20:52,607 --> 00:20:56,027
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{kachi}It's not about winning or losing,
but for friendship between teams.</font>

293
00:20:57,227 --> 00:20:59,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">How does it sound ?</font>

294
00:20:59,587 --> 00:21:03,017
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We don't have any reason to refuse, so...</font>

295
00:21:03,017 --> 00:21:04,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Then, it's decided.</font>

296
00:21:05,927 --> 00:21:09,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Let us practice as much as we can today.</font>

297
00:21:10,257 --> 00:21:12,227
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We'll follow proper street racing manners.</font>

298
00:21:27,257 --> 00:21:28,387
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Iketani...</font>

299
00:21:28,387 --> 00:21:33,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yeah, their formality is all fake. 
That was an outright challenge.</font>

300
00:21:33,207 --> 00:21:35,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">No need to chicken out. Let's go.</font>

301
00:21:35,507 --> 00:21:37,077
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">They'd better not underestimate the locals !</font>

302
00:21:37,077 --> 00:21:38,767
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Let's kick their ass !</font>

303
00:21:50,507 --> 00:21:53,097
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Iketani, can we go, too ?</font>

304
00:21:53,997 --> 00:21:56,997
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Sorry, but I can't let anyone 
ride along when I drive seriously.</font>

305
00:21:57,407 --> 00:21:58,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Wait here.</font>

306
00:22:08,697 --> 00:22:11,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Man, I wanted to go...</font>

307
00:22:45,927 --> 00:22:48,677
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What...? 
They're already that far ahead ?</font>

308
00:22:49,107 --> 00:22:51,517
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'm doing my best, 
and still can't keep up !</font>

309
00:22:59,657 --> 00:23:01,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">This is just too sad.</font>

310
00:23:01,597 --> 00:23:05,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Why are we the only ones who 
don't have a car at a time like this ?!</font>

311
00:23:08,207 --> 00:23:10,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Hey, Itsuki...</font>

312
00:23:10,207 --> 00:23:12,147
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">...is this fun ?</font>

313
00:23:13,157 --> 00:23:15,787
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Street racers are strange.</font>

314
00:23:15,787 --> 00:23:18,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Why do they go nuts{bananas}
 over something like this ?</font>

315
00:23:19,557 --> 00:23:21,647
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Takumi, don't you feel anything ?!</font>

316
00:23:22,457 --> 00:23:25,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Cars zooming by one after another !</font>

317
00:23:25,257 --> 00:23:27,867
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The exhaust note, the squealing sound...</font>

318
00:23:27,867 --> 00:23:29,627
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The smell of burning rubber...</font>

319
00:23:29,627 --> 00:23:32,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Don't you get excited
 by seeing this in person ?</font>

320
00:23:32,657 --> 00:23:35,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">My tension is so high.</font>

321
00:23:39,357 --> 00:23:41,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Get excited...?</font></font>

322
00:23:48,307 --> 00:23:50,197
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Akina is full of losers.</font></font>

323
00:23:53,017 --> 00:23:54,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Going that fast ?!</font>

324
00:24:01,857 --> 00:24:02,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Iketani...</font>

325
00:24:02,807 --> 00:24:04,777
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">If they can do it, so can I.</font>

326
00:24:18,207 --> 00:24:22,127
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Downhill driving is tough...really tough.</font></font>

327
00:24:23,407 --> 00:24:27,627
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Akina's familiar corners are
 showing their vicious side.</font></font>

328
00:24:37,357 --> 00:24:41,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">I couldn't even see the tails of the Akagi guys 
even though I pushed myself to such a scary level...</font></font>

329
00:24:42,507 --> 00:24:44,747
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Is this all the technique I've got ?</font></font>

330
00:24:49,927 --> 00:24:54,177
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I feel hopeless after seeing that.</font>

331
00:24:54,177 --> 00:24:56,897
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I can't catch them no matter how hard I try.</font>

332
00:24:56,897 --> 00:24:59,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">They're fundamentally different.</font>

333
00:24:59,707 --> 00:25:03,057
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We're getting pounded on our home ground.</font>

334
00:25:03,057 --> 00:25:05,237
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Are the Red Suns that good ?</font>

335
00:25:18,607 --> 00:25:19,667
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Iketani.</font>

336
00:25:20,507 --> 00:25:22,347
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He hasn't quit yet ?</font>

337
00:25:23,007 --> 00:25:24,397
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Is he alright ?</font>

338
00:25:26,607 --> 00:25:29,047
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He was pushing really hard earlier.</font>

339
00:25:32,277 --> 00:25:34,197
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Akina is our mountain.</font></font>

340
00:25:34,407 --> 00:25:36,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">I'll show you the pride of the locals.</font></font>

341
00:25:49,897 --> 00:25:51,047
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What was that ?</font>

342
00:25:51,047 --> 00:25:51,997
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Someone crashed !</font>

343
00:26:08,647 --> 00:26:09,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I see.</font>

344
00:26:10,257 --> 00:26:14,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He was lucky his injuries weren't serious.</font>

345
00:26:14,157 --> 00:26:15,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Right.</font>

346
00:26:15,507 --> 00:26:20,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Tell Iketani that we can
 postpone the Saturday event.</font>

347
00:26:20,887 --> 00:26:27,357
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">But even if he's still up for it, you guys can't defeat me
 unless you bring your secret weapon, the Eight-Six.</font>

348
00:26:28,597 --> 00:26:30,817
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'll drive the downhill on the event day.</font>

349
00:26:30,817 --> 00:26:35,927
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{konomae}I was caught off guard the other day because I wasn't mentally prepared, and not familiar with the course.</font>

350
00:26:35,927 --> 00:26:38,217
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I won't lose to the same opponent.</font>

351
00:26:39,197 --> 00:26:40,047
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Got it.</font>

352
00:26:53,137 --> 00:26:54,097
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">This is it.</font>

353
00:26:57,417 --> 00:26:58,277
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Howdy.</font>

354
00:26:58,877 --> 00:27:03,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I've finally found the Eight-Six driver, Akina's very best.</font>

355
00:27:09,267 --> 00:27:14,357
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Come to think of it, Akagi had plenty 
of skilled street racers back in the old days.</font>

356
00:27:14,357 --> 00:27:18,897
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{kedo}But I'm not the one who
 beat the Akagi driver's pants off.</font>

357
00:27:18,897 --> 00:27:23,417
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That can't be. There's no other person
 who delivers tofu with an Eight-Six.</font>

358
00:27:23,417 --> 00:27:28,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Even if it was me,
 I wouldn't race as a helper.</font>

359
00:27:30,237 --> 00:27:34,027
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">An old man like me 
should know his place, right ?</font>

360
00:27:35,387 --> 00:27:38,757
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's an issue the younger
 folks have to solve themselves.</font>

361
00:27:42,807 --> 00:27:51,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'm a street racer who grew up on Akina, 
so I can clearly see the Akagi guys are mocking us.</font>

362
00:27:51,207 --> 00:27:53,977
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{sorega}That frustrates me most.</font>

363
00:27:53,977 --> 00:27:58,597
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I want to show them Akina has skilled drivers.</font>

364
00:27:59,307 --> 00:28:03,927
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You can do it, since you beat
 Takahashi Keisuke once before.</font>

365
00:28:06,887 --> 00:28:09,017
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Here, your fried tofu. 140 yen.</font>

366
00:28:10,957 --> 00:28:13,777
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Go home.
 Sorry that I can't be of any help.</font>

367
00:28:18,747 --> 00:28:23,087
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I won't give up, Mr. Fujiwara. 
I'll come back tomorrow.</font>

368
00:28:31,087 --> 00:28:34,957
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Oh well, it wasn't me, really.</font>

369
00:28:36,287 --> 00:28:38,497
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I can't hate a guy like him.</font>

370
00:28:48,017 --> 00:28:54,877
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The thing is, I have 
something I must tell you, Takumi.</font>

371
00:28:56,567 --> 00:28:57,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What is it ?</font>

372
00:28:59,957 --> 00:29:00,897
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I...</font>

373
00:29:04,927 --> 00:29:07,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I bought a new bathing suit.</font>

374
00:29:07,607 --> 00:29:09,577
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's super pretty.</font>

375
00:29:12,207 --> 00:29:14,847
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What ?
 That's all you wanted to say ?</font>

376
00:29:14,847 --> 00:29:16,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Right on !</font>

377
00:29:16,207 --> 00:29:20,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Good grief. I had to brace 
myself for what you might say.</font>

378
00:29:20,257 --> 00:29:24,667
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">But I'm so happy
 that I had to tell someone.</font>

379
00:29:27,317 --> 00:29:30,137
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Do you wanna see it ? 
What color do you think it is ?</font>

380
00:29:30,687 --> 00:29:31,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You wanna see sooner ?</font>

381
00:29:33,007 --> 00:29:35,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Honestly...yes.</font>

382
00:29:35,557 --> 00:29:38,617
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You can see it all you want,
 once we get to the beach.</font>

383
00:29:39,387 --> 00:29:41,357
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Save the fun until then.</font>

384
00:29:42,257 --> 00:29:47,277
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What about next Sunday ? 
Are you free ?</font>

385
00:29:47,657 --> 00:29:50,057
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Next Sunday ?</font>

386
00:29:50,057 --> 00:29:52,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Fine. I don't have to work that day.</font>

387
00:29:52,557 --> 00:29:55,587
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Okay, that's it then.
 It's a promise, okay ?</font>

388
00:29:55,587 --> 00:30:01,857
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You must not break it, because I hate
 smokers and people who break promises.</font>

389
00:30:01,857 --> 00:30:03,697
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What're you going to do if it rains ?</font>

390
00:30:03,697 --> 00:30:07,077
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We'll just improvise. 
So, it's next Sunday, okay ?</font>

391
00:30:15,257 --> 00:30:20,597
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">I'm becoming more and 
more interested in Mogi lately.</font></font>

392
00:30:24,457 --> 00:30:28,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Street racers hate to lose 
because of their strong pride.</font>

393
00:30:28,657 --> 00:30:31,857
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{toiuka}Actually, we have nothing else we're good at.</font>

394
00:30:31,857 --> 00:30:36,867
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{dakara}So, losing on a familiar 
course humiliates us the most.</font>

395
00:30:37,387 --> 00:30:43,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{jimoto}The locals mustn't lose to outsiders.
That's the street racer's code.</font>

396
00:30:50,437 --> 00:30:53,687
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'll come back. 
Your fried tofu tastes good.</font>

397
00:31:11,347 --> 00:31:15,047
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Because of my poor skills, 
you have to bear this pain.</font></font>

398
00:31:15,907 --> 00:31:18,577
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Sorry, Silvia. Forgive me.</font></font>

399
00:31:20,857 --> 00:31:24,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">I hope you get repaired 
and come back to me soon.</font></font>

400
00:31:24,207 --> 00:31:26,267
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">We can race together again.</font></font>

401
00:31:28,707 --> 00:31:32,877
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yuichi, because you filled them full
 of bullshit, I get a visitor every day.</font>

402
00:31:32,877 --> 00:31:37,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{Gips}That young Iketani guy with his
 arm in a cast limps back and forth.</font>

403
00:31:37,607 --> 00:31:40,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He's so pitiful.
 I can't stand watching him.</font>

404
00:31:40,407 --> 00:31:42,467
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Iketani is a nice guy.</font>

405
00:31:42,467 --> 00:31:45,467
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">If you feel pity,
why don't you race for him ?</font>

406
00:31:45,467 --> 00:31:49,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">No thanks. Adults shouldn't 
meddle in fights between kids.</font>

407
00:31:49,157 --> 00:31:50,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's my policy.</font>

408
00:31:50,807 --> 00:31:53,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You're still childish inside.</font>

409
00:31:53,407 --> 00:31:54,437
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Shut up.</font>

410
00:31:55,077 --> 00:31:59,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Well then, why don't you 
send a kid to a kids' fight ?</font>

411
00:32:01,647 --> 00:32:03,717
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Are you talking about Takumi ?</font>

412
00:32:03,717 --> 00:32:06,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Right.
 He's pretty good, isn't he ?</font>

413
00:32:06,547 --> 00:32:08,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">On the downhill, yeah.</font>

414
00:32:09,007 --> 00:32:10,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">But not as good as me, though...</font>

415
00:32:10,927 --> 00:32:13,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You get competitive so easily.</font>

416
00:32:13,407 --> 00:32:18,447
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I don't know how he got it, 
but he has a stubborn side...</font>

417
00:32:18,447 --> 00:32:22,967
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{hashire}...so he wouldn't race even if I told him to.{ell him to do so.}</font>

418
00:32:26,207 --> 00:32:27,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Hey...</font>

419
00:32:27,767 --> 00:32:30,327
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Can I use the car next Sunday ?</font>

420
00:32:30,327 --> 00:32:31,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Sunday ?</font>

421
00:32:31,907 --> 00:32:32,777
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">No.</font>

422
00:32:32,777 --> 00:32:34,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Why not ?
The shop is closed on Sunday.</font>

423
00:32:35,847 --> 00:32:38,827
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I need it because I have a commerce meeting.</font>

424
00:32:39,557 --> 00:32:43,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Seriously ? 
I really need to use the car that day.</font>

425
00:32:43,867 --> 00:32:47,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'll be in trouble if I can't use it, 
even though it's just a clunker.</font>

426
00:32:47,007 --> 00:32:49,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Man, this isn't good.</font>

427
00:32:52,257 --> 00:32:53,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's about a girl, isn't it ?</font>

428
00:32:54,707 --> 00:32:58,237
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So what ? I'll use the
 car without asking, okay ?</font>

429
00:32:59,457 --> 00:33:01,597
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You can't drive a car without the key.</font>

430
00:33:01,597 --> 00:33:04,387
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Maybe I should hang it around my neck.</font>

431
00:33:04,997 --> 00:33:06,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You dirty old...</font>

432
00:33:08,597 --> 00:33:13,167
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Well, if you're that desperate,
 I may reconsider.</font>

433
00:33:13,167 --> 00:33:15,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">But I have a condition.</font>

434
00:33:15,707 --> 00:33:16,747
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">A condition ?</font>

435
00:33:18,067 --> 00:33:24,787
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Tomorrow night, you take the car and beat a
 big mouth who claims to be the fastest on Akagi...</font>

436
00:33:25,457 --> 00:33:26,857
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">...on the downhill of Akina.</font>

437
00:33:27,907 --> 00:33:29,377
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{What ?} Why ?</font>

438
00:33:29,377 --> 00:33:32,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Then I'll let you use the
 car with no strings attached...</font>

439
00:33:32,257 --> 00:33:34,927
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">...with a full tank of gas to boot.</font>

440
00:33:35,317 --> 00:33:37,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Full tank of gas...</font>

441
00:33:38,337 --> 00:33:42,077
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Damn, that condition is so tempting.</font></font>

442
00:33:50,247 --> 00:33:52,987
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What ? Are you sure ?</font>

443
00:33:52,987 --> 00:33:56,577
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I may be able to go to Mt. Akina tonight.</font>

444
00:33:56,577 --> 00:33:57,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Thank...</font>

445
00:33:58,977 --> 00:34:01,477
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Thank you, Mr. Fujiwara.</font>

446
00:34:01,927 --> 00:34:03,737
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Hey, don't die on me.</font>

447
00:34:04,957 --> 00:34:08,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The time attack begins 
at 10 o'clock. I'll be waiting.</font>

448
00:34:09,007 --> 00:34:11,757
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I can't guarantee it yet.</font>

449
00:34:11,757 --> 00:34:16,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">If my Eight-Six doesn't show
 up on time, please give up.</font>

450
00:34:17,307 --> 00:34:19,077
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You'll have to resolve the matter yourself.</font>

451
00:34:19,467 --> 00:34:23,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I trust you.
 I know you've decided to go.</font>

452
00:34:24,007 --> 00:34:27,577
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Our entire team will be waiting for you, Mr. Fujiwara.</font>

453
00:34:28,487 --> 00:34:29,617
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Thank you !</font>

454
00:34:33,207 --> 00:34:35,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">If Takumi whines, maybe I should race.</font>

455
00:34:43,207 --> 00:34:45,867
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So many cars are headed for Mt. Akina.</font>

456
00:34:47,007 --> 00:34:49,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Akina versus Akagi.</font>

457
00:34:49,157 --> 00:34:54,377
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Akagi's fastest RX-7 and the
 unnamed downhill specialist of Akina...</font>

458
00:34:54,377 --> 00:34:56,167
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{kono}This battle can't be missed.</font>

459
00:34:57,747 --> 00:35:01,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">And then, hungry cars 
come one after another.</font>

460
00:35:01,307 --> 00:35:03,867
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'd better leave the station open late.</font>

461
00:35:31,167 --> 00:35:34,847
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The Red Suns have already
 dispatched their course marshals.</font>

462
00:35:34,847 --> 00:35:36,357
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Besides...</font>

463
00:35:36,357 --> 00:35:40,997
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Look at the size of the gallery. 
I've never seen so many on Akina.</font>

464
00:35:42,337 --> 00:35:46,737
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Iketani, can we really trust 
your story about the Eight-Six ?</font>

465
00:35:46,737 --> 00:35:48,267
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yeah, he will come.</font>

466
00:35:48,947 --> 00:35:54,877
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Takahashi Keisuke's FD3S is easily making 350HP.</font>

467
00:35:54,877 --> 00:35:58,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{ikura}Even on the downhill,
an Eight-Six is no match...</font>

468
00:35:58,707 --> 00:36:00,347
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Trust me.</font>

469
00:36:00,347 --> 00:36:02,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What if he doesn't come ?</font>

470
00:36:03,257 --> 00:36:04,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Then...</font>

471
00:36:05,107 --> 00:36:06,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Kenji, you race.</font>

472
00:36:06,407 --> 00:36:07,397
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What ?!</font>

473
00:36:07,397 --> 00:36:09,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">See the gallery ?</font>

474
00:36:09,207 --> 00:36:11,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">For the sake of the team,
 push hard, like there's no tomorrow.</font>

475
00:36:11,557 --> 00:36:15,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">N...no way, this can't be happening...</font>

476
00:36:15,207 --> 00:36:17,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'm not very{really} confident.</font>

477
00:36:24,697 --> 00:36:25,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Keisuke ! {Girl2 So cool ! GIRL3 He's so cool.}</font>

478
00:36:25,657 --> 00:36:27,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">So cool !</font>

479
00:36:27,007 --> 00:36:28,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He's so cool !</font>

480
00:36:35,037 --> 00:36:37,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's about time. 
Let's start the event.</font>

481
00:36:38,927 --> 00:36:42,377
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The time attack begins at 10 o'clock. 
Let's drive freely until then.</font>

482
00:36:43,117 --> 00:36:43,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Right.</font>

483
00:36:44,907 --> 00:36:47,717
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The size of the gallery seems big.
 So let's have fun.</font>

484
00:36:48,677 --> 00:36:50,337
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Show time, huh ?</font>

485
00:36:52,387 --> 00:36:53,417
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">There they are.</font>

486
00:36:58,707 --> 00:37:01,547
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The Red Suns guys are pretty good at drifting.</font>

487
00:37:01,547 --> 00:37:04,047
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">They don't miss the clipping point.</font>

488
00:37:20,117 --> 00:37:21,337
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's...</font>

489
00:37:21,337 --> 00:37:23,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">...the sound of a rotary. 
They're coming.</font>

490
00:37:27,207 --> 00:37:29,747
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Takahashi, the Rotary Brothers.</font>

491
00:37:33,157 --> 00:37:35,787
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's pointed to the left before the right hander.</font>

492
00:37:37,787 --> 00:37:40,487
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Takahashi Keisuke's FD is so dynamic.</font>

493
00:37:41,017 --> 00:37:42,927
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Next is Takahashi Ryosuke's FC.</font>

494
00:37:46,277 --> 00:37:49,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">No way ! He began a
 straight drift from so far away !</font>

495
00:37:49,457 --> 00:37:51,127
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Can he reach here ?</font>

496
00:37:55,467 --> 00:37:58,017
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He kept the drift all through the corner.</font>

497
00:37:58,017 --> 00:37:59,437
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">How did he do that ?</font>

498
00:38:08,207 --> 00:38:09,117
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Not yet ?</font>

499
00:38:15,597 --> 00:38:18,197
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What an awesome parallel drift.</font>

500
00:38:18,197 --> 00:38:20,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">They're in perfect sync.</font>

501
00:38:20,457 --> 00:38:25,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Their claim of "the fastest in Akagi" 
isn't a sham. Their skills are real.</font>

502
00:38:29,477 --> 00:38:30,997
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The Eight-Six hasn't arrived yet.</font>

503
00:38:34,557 --> 00:38:36,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Please come, Mr. Fujiwara.</font></font>

504
00:38:41,207 --> 00:38:44,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">What a waste. 
These are just for show.</font></font>

505
00:38:44,657 --> 00:38:47,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">My driving is different when I go for time.</font></font>

506
00:38:48,907 --> 00:38:51,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Akina doesn't have any worthy opponents.</font></font>

507
00:38:51,507 --> 00:38:54,287
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Come out, Eight-Six, so I can prove it.</font></font>

508
00:39:06,007 --> 00:39:08,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">No cup of water today ?</font>

509
00:39:08,207 --> 00:39:11,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Why would you need it ? 
You're not carrying tofu.</font>

510
00:39:12,327 --> 00:39:14,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Just enjoy it, okay ?</font>

511
00:39:14,407 --> 00:39:19,087
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Enjoyment is supposed to be fun, right ?
 But I'm not really into this.</font>

512
00:39:19,087 --> 00:39:21,447
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What ? You aren't confident ?</font>

513
00:39:21,447 --> 00:39:23,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I don't mean that.</font>

514
00:39:24,097 --> 00:39:26,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Just drive as usual, and you won't lose.</font>

515
00:39:27,027 --> 00:39:28,217
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Is that right ?</font>

516
00:39:29,217 --> 00:39:29,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'm off.</font>

517
00:39:44,697 --> 00:39:45,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Mr. Fujiwara...</font>

518
00:39:47,007 --> 00:39:50,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Brother, the Eight-Six hasn't come.</font>

519
00:39:50,207 --> 00:39:54,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I thought it would show up,
 but what a disappointment.</font>

520
00:39:54,007 --> 00:39:55,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">This pisses me off.</font>

521
00:39:58,357 --> 00:40:00,147
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Did you finish checking 
for debris on the course ?</font>

