00:51:31,907 --> 00:51:35,717
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I don't know. That Eight-Six 
couldn't have cleared the corner.</font>

691
00:51:36,507 --> 00:51:43,627
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">He let the tires grab the gutter 
and turned at an abnormal speed.</font></font>

692
00:51:44,787 --> 00:51:48,897
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">It's a simple idea, but not
 a trick anyone can pull off.</font></font>

693
00:51:48,897 --> 00:51:52,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">There're some over-the-top
 crazy drivers out there.</font></font>

694
00:51:52,007 --> 00:51:54,437
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">I've found some more fun.</font></font>

695
00:51:58,887 --> 00:51:59,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Here it comes.</font>

696
00:51:59,657 --> 00:52:00,287
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Which one ?</font>

697
00:52:01,837 --> 00:52:02,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The Eight-Six...?</font>

698
00:52:23,107 --> 00:52:26,857
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That air-headed Takumi won !</font>

699
00:52:26,857 --> 00:52:30,077
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">With seven seconds of advantage. 
This's way too cool.</font>

700
00:52:30,477 --> 00:52:33,337
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I felt myself going pale, and now
 I have goose bumps all over.</font>

701
00:52:33,337 --> 00:52:36,317
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Why are you crying, you idiot ?</font>

702
00:52:37,257 --> 00:52:40,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I don't know, but I'm just so happy.</font>

703
00:52:41,157 --> 00:52:46,537
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We should ask Takumi all kinds of stuff,
 like drift control and line taking.</font>

704
00:52:46,537 --> 00:52:47,247
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Right.</font>

705
00:52:48,127 --> 00:52:51,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We should put a Speed Stars sticker 
on the Eight-Six before he notices.{knows it.}</font>

706
00:52:51,907 --> 00:52:54,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'll be honored to do that.</font>

707
00:52:54,107 --> 00:52:55,757
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Really ? Okay, you do it.</font>

708
00:52:55,757 --> 00:52:58,047
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">How could Keisuke lose ?</font>

709
00:52:58,047 --> 00:53:02,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We assembled this gallery to promote 
the Red Suns, but it backfired, didn't it ?</font>

710
00:53:02,807 --> 00:53:06,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">We underestimated Akina.
 I didn't expect a street racer like him.</font>

711
00:53:06,707 --> 00:53:09,637
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The rumors will spread tomorrow.</font>

712
00:53:09,637 --> 00:53:12,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yeah, we'll win on the uphill...</font>

713
00:53:12,657 --> 00:53:16,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">...but this event essentially
 ends with a Red Suns defeat.</font>

714
00:53:21,107 --> 00:53:24,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">I must admit, things like this
 do happen in mountain passes.</font></font>

715
00:53:25,717 --> 00:53:28,677
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">That Eight-Six is interesting.</font></font>

716
00:53:51,577 --> 00:53:53,307
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I accept my defeat.</font>

717
00:53:55,767 --> 00:53:57,157
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You must keep winning.</font>

718
00:53:57,157 --> 00:54:01,977
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You can't lose to any street
 racers until I beat you. Got it ?</font>

719
00:54:01,977 --> 00:54:04,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I have no reason to take orders from you.</font>

720
00:54:04,657 --> 00:54:07,367
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Besides, I'm not a street racer.</font>

721
00:54:07,367 --> 00:54:09,107
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Are you being sarcastic ?</font>

722
00:54:09,107 --> 00:54:12,997
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{aredake}You must have practiced really
 hard to achieve that level of skill.</font>

723
00:54:12,997 --> 00:54:14,637
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You wouldn't have done that, unless you like it.</font>

724
00:54:14,637 --> 00:54:17,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I don't drive because I like it.</font>

725
00:54:17,207 --> 00:54:19,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I have no choice because I have 
to help my father's business.</font>

726
00:54:19,657 --> 00:54:22,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{tanoshii}I had to find something interesting
 to do because it's boring.</font>

727
00:54:22,657 --> 00:54:26,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{tanoshii}I also want to return home quickly, 
so I drive as fast as possible.</font>

728
00:54:26,697 --> 00:54:30,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{dakara}So I never wanted to 
improve my driving skills.</font>

729
00:54:31,707 --> 00:54:33,477
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{dakara} You don't understand.</font>

730
00:54:33,477 --> 00:54:34,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Don't be ridiculous !</font>

731
00:54:34,907 --> 00:54:37,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You're the one who doesn't get it !</font>

732
00:54:37,257 --> 00:54:40,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You must like driving !</font>

733
00:54:41,407 --> 00:54:44,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{kore}You should realize it after tonight.</font>

734
00:54:44,457 --> 00:54:49,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">{kuruma}If you like to drive a car, 
that's enough to be a street racer.</font>

735
00:54:49,707 --> 00:54:53,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">If you're a street racer, 
be proud of the skills you've got !</font>

736
00:55:13,207 --> 00:55:17,217
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I like to drive a car...?</font>

737
00:55:33,617 --> 00:55:35,217
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">That was strange.</font></font>

738
00:55:36,257 --> 00:55:40,327
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">The RX-7 in front of me
 was getting closer and closer.</font></font>

739
00:55:40,327 --> 00:55:43,527
<font size="42" color="#ffff00"><font color="#ffffff">Before I knew it I was enjoying the chase.</font></font>

740
00:55:47,207 --> 00:55:48,477
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I had enough fun swimming.</font>

741
00:55:49,107 --> 00:55:52,117
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The ocean is definitely 
better than the swimming pool.</font>

742
00:55:52,117 --> 00:55:54,007
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Did you have fun, Takumi ?</font>

743
00:55:55,257 --> 00:55:56,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Yeah.</font>

744
00:55:56,507 --> 00:55:57,927
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's nice that we came, right ?</font>

745
00:56:00,557 --> 00:56:05,817
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Takumi, you're pretty good at driving.</font>

746
00:56:05,817 --> 00:56:06,767
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Am I ?</font>

747
00:56:07,767 --> 00:56:10,657
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I tend to get motion sick.</font>

748
00:56:10,657 --> 00:56:15,037
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">But your driving didn't make me feel sick.</font>

749
00:56:16,887 --> 00:56:19,857
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I like this car.</font>

750
00:56:20,657 --> 00:56:22,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">It's little and cute.</font>

751
00:56:22,557 --> 00:56:23,707
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">What's it called ?</font>

752
00:56:24,217 --> 00:56:25,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Trueno.</font>

753
00:56:25,557 --> 00:56:26,607
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Trueno ?</font>

754
00:56:28,007 --> 00:56:29,927
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Let me ride in your Trueno again.</font>

755
00:56:31,647 --> 00:56:32,417
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Sure.</font>

756
00:56:42,037 --> 00:56:45,267
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Cute, she says. 
What're you gonna do ?</font>

757
00:56:54,657 --> 00:56:57,547
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I heard Takumi was extraordinary.</font>

758
00:56:57,547 --> 00:57:01,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Iketani and the others were going
 on and on about it all morning.</font>

759
00:57:01,907 --> 00:57:03,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He's nothing special.</font>

760
00:57:05,157 --> 00:57:07,847
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">The level of the kids these days must be low.</font>

761
00:57:07,847 --> 00:57:09,907
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'm looking forward to his future.</font>

762
00:57:09,907 --> 00:57:13,977
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You might not be able to 
stay so confident much longer.</font>

763
00:57:17,127 --> 00:57:19,207
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's impossible.</font>

764
00:57:19,207 --> 00:57:20,617
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Oh, really ?</font>

765
00:57:28,757 --> 00:57:29,567
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Here ya go.</font>

766
00:57:34,007 --> 00:57:34,807
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Dad.</font>

767
00:57:37,087 --> 00:57:41,867
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">When I drove this car, 
everyone seemed happy.</font>

768
00:57:48,957 --> 00:57:51,507
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Maybe I didn't know I liked cars.</font>

769
00:57:53,707 --> 00:57:54,557
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Is that right ?</font>

770
00:57:55,127 --> 00:58:01,457
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I might become a better driver 
than you in two or three years.</font>

771
00:58:01,457 --> 00:58:03,407
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">You're ten years too early to say that.</font>

772
00:58:08,907 --> 00:58:09,927
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I'm off.</font>

773
00:58:09,927 --> 00:58:10,867
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">Okay.</font>

