<font face="Qlassik Bold" size="40">{Ima kimi wo, ima toki wo koete}Now I leave you and my past behind.</font>

795
01:01:11,907 --> 01:01:21,607
<font face="Qlassik Bold" size="40">{Hashiridasu omoi wa tomerarenai}As my passion begins to race forward it's unstoppable.</font>

796
01:01:21,607 --> 01:01:25,107
<font face="Qlassik Bold" size="40">{Yamanai}Forever.</font>

797
01:01:29,037 --> 01:01:31,957
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I want to drive like Takumi.</font>

798
01:01:33,307 --> 01:01:36,417
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">That's a GT-R R32.</font>

799
01:01:37,557 --> 01:01:41,257
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">I pay respect to the R badge, but I won't yield.</font>

800
01:01:52,207 --> 01:01:55,187
<font size="42" color="#ffff00">He passed me from the outside so easily.</font>

801
